"<systemitem role=\"package\">topgit</systemitem> : gestionnaire de file de "
"correctifs Git ;"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
msgid ""
"<systemitem role=\"package\">svn-buildpackage</systemitem>: helper programs "
"to maintain Debian packages with Subversion."
msgstr ""
"<systemitem role=\"package\">svn-buildpackage</systemitem> : assistants pour "
"la maintenance de paquets Debian en dépôt Subversion ;"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
msgid ""
"<systemitem role=\"package\">cvs-buildpackage</systemitem>: A set of Debian "
"package scripts for CVS source trees."
msgstr ""
"<systemitem role=\"package\">cvs-buildpackage</systemitem> : scripts pour "
"paquets Debian en dépôt CVS."

