"\">&uploadqueue;</ulink>, you can fix this by manually uploading GPG signed "
"<filename>*.commands</filename> file to there with <command>ftp</command>.  "
"<placeholder type=\"footnote\" id=\"0\"/> For example, use <filename>hello."
"commands</filename>:"
